### Test Google OAuth Flow
### Sử dụng với REST Client extension trong VS Code

### 1. Test Normal Login (để so sánh)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Test Google OAuth Callback
### Lưu ý: Thay YOUR_AUTHORIZATION_CODE bằng code thực từ Google
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/google/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "YOUR_AUTHORIZATION_CODE",
  "redirectUri": "http://localhost:3000/auth/google/callback"
}

### 3. Test với JWT Token (sau khi login)
### Thay YOUR_JWT_TOKEN bằng token nhận được
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 4. Health Check - UserService
GET http://localhost:8085/actuator/health

### 5. Health Check - API Gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
